{{Infobox College |name=Centro de Aperfeiçoamento Técnico Agro-Pecuário |image= |image_size= |image_name= |caption= | pushpin_map = Sao Tome | map_size = | pushpin_map_alt = | pushpin_relief = | pushpin_label = | pushpin_label_position = |coordinates = {{Coord|0|17|45|N|6|39|50|E|display=it}} |address= |city=[[Piedade, São Tomé and Príncipe|Piedade]] |country=[[São Tomé and Príncipe]] |native_name= |established=1988 |teachers= |students= |website= }} '''Centro de Aperfeiçoamento Técnico Agro-Pecuário''' ('''CATAP''', Portuguese for: "Centre for technical improvement of agriculture and animal husbandry") is an agricultural training centre in [[São Tomé and Príncipe]].<ref>[http://www.fao.org/sao-tome-e-principe/noticias/detail-events/fr/c/898118/ FAO en Sao Tomé-et-Principe], 21 June 2017 {{fr icon}}</ref> It is located the village of [[Piedade, São Tomé and Príncipe|Piedade]], [[Mé-Zóchi District]].<ref>[http://www.fao.org/docrep/pdf/010/a1250e/annexes/CountryReports/SaoTomePrincipe.pdf Rapport National São Tomé e Príncipe], Direcção da Pecuaria (2005), p. 66 {{fr icon}}</ref> It was established in 1988 by the Italian NGO Nuova Frontiera,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.unicef.org/saotome/nf/interven.htm|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912234331/https://www.unicef.org/saotome/nf/interven.htm|archive-date=12 September 2017|title=Nuova Frontiera, Areas de intervenção|publisher=[[UNESCO]]|dead-url=yes}}</ref> with support from the [[European Union]], the Republic of São Tomé and Príncipe, the [[World Food Programme]] and the Canada Fund for Local Initiatives.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.unicef.org/saotome/nf/projecto.htm|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912234507/https://www.unicef.org/saotome/nf/projecto.htm|archive-date=12 September 2017|title=Nuova Frontiera, Areas de intervenção|publisher=[[UNESCO]]|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
